# Development Mode Active

This file indicates the application is in development mode.

When this file exists, AI assistants should:
1. Automatically update .zencoder/rules/repo.md when making code changes
2. Document new features, database changes, and functionality directly in repo.md
3. Avoid creating separate markdown documentation files
4. Maintain a comprehensive development log in the main repository documentation

Remove this file when moving to production to disable automatic documentation updates.